projects.name: Care Connect
projects.description: Conceptualized, designed, and developed an online Doctor Booking application. Used HTML, CSS, and JavaScript for the front end and TypeScript, NodeJs for the back end with MySql for the database. Ensured a smooth user experience with responsive feedback and client-side validation.

projects.name: Pharma Flow
projects.description: Developed an online pharmacy management system using Java, JSP, and JDBC. Ensured a user-friendly interface for online medicine ordering with client-side validation. Maintained a clear dependency chain and organized file system for scalable and maintainable code.

projects.name: Gym Genius
projects.description: Developed a Gym Management System using C++. Handled member registration, attendance tracking, and billing. Utilized skills in object-oriented programming, file handling, and data structures.

experiences.description: Developed a website using Django Framework for the backend and DB Browser for the database. Implemented features to allow users to purchase products directly from farmers, ensuring a user-friendly interface. Worked closely with a team to ensure a clear dependency chain in application logic and file system organization. Gained experience in validating user actions on the client side and providing responsive feedback.
